auction.disclaimers:
WARNING - PLEASE READ THIS CAREFULLY BEFORE BIDDING!

  • Pickup time windows are fixed and limited. You will be required to select a pickup window prior to the auction pickup. Please be sure to select a time slot that you are certain you will be able to attend.
  • Claims for refund can be made only in certain limited circumstances. When an error in the lot description has occurred on an item you purchased, let our pickup lead know immediately so we may rectify it. Transparency is our aim in the sale of the "as is where is" used goods.
  • MaxSold does not arrange shipping; however, you can make your own arrangements at your own risk
  • Current bids cannot be changed or removed once submitted and each one is a promise that you will honor the bid and all the terms.
